have in mind on these issues dole said we will have plenty of 
time next year to address each of them 
but republicans and democrats alike each have a political agenda 
that could keep them in washington well into october senate 
majority leader robert byrd dwva is telling colleagues to plan 
on weekend work and a midoctober escape 
whats keeping congress in town in addition to some money 
bills a bipartisan overhaul of the welfare system and other 
