love canal an abandoned waterway was used by the hooker 
chemical co to dispose of thousands of pounds of chemical wastes 
in the 1940s the company made herbicides and pesticides 
in the 1950s the canal and its contents were filled in and 
homes and an elementary school were built on top it wasnt until 
the early 1970s that residents began to notice foul smells in their 
basements and oily puddles in their yards 
