serious condition since he vomited blood on sept 19 on saturday 
his temperature reached 1026 degrees but doctors were able to 
bring his fever down with antibiotics 
palace officials have refused to confirm or deny news reports 
that the emperor has cancer and have urged the media to refrain 
from such speculation because it might dishearten the emperor who 
they say is conscious and has been watching television 
