announce their new policies and what they say depends of course 
on the questions they are asked but the impression we got of the 
bushdukakis debate is that the position of the united states in 
the world seems to be changing 
we hope the next debate will take up japanus relations and 
issues related to americas position in asia 
</TEXT>
